title: The Fizik Vento Antares Adaptive Saddle is Upgraded with 3D-Printed Cushioning
content:
Fizik's low-profile flat-topped road racing saddle gets the Adaptive treatment with a 3D-Printed lattice developed in collaboration with Carbon; yours for just $259.99 USD.

Read the full article at The Fizik Vento Antares Adaptive Saddle is Upgraded with 3D-Printed Cushioning on Velo.
author: Jessie-May Morgan
